{"type":"message","id":"75416fca","parentId":"01ab76cc","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:08:59.971Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session found is the cron job itself. The session's last message was an assistant message about calling sessions_list. There are no other active user conversations in the last 5 minutes. This cron job session itself doesn't count as an active user conversation - it's just the cron task running.\n\nI should perform the autonomous learning task. Let me:\n1. Search for latest news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services\n2. Compile 3-5 key pieces of information\n3. Save to /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\nLet me use the web search skill to find this information.","thinkingSignature":"ed5beb052526282f362e56039753f04ba03e0580857d2d758849663ed1799cf3"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到没有活跃对话（当前仅存在 cron 任务自身的内部会话，无用户消息）。开始执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_424d2juaqnxl_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":899,"output":205,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45085,"cost":{"input":0.0002697,"output":0.00024599999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00183513}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775077734189}}
{"type":"message","id":"357baddf","parentId":"75416fca","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:08:59.977Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_424d2juaqnxl_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775077739974}}
{"type":"message","id":"8e8ac8f4","parentId":"357baddf","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:09:04.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to search for information about enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services. Let me run multiple searches.","thinkingSignature":"6fd86d90b097ebac4a911403aa1e7e917107e8d2000ff8856fe35fcf7b450936"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fg9aw41niy2x_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新趋势政策\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fg9aw41niy2x_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 弱电工程 行业动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fg9aw41niy2x_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 网络系统集成 市场规模 2026\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1619,"output":201,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45801,"cost":{"input":0.0004857,"output":0.00024119999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00204633}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775077739977}}
